---
title: Quick BBQ-Glazed Chicken Strips with Creamy Potato Mash & Slaw
description: This recipe might sound like it's involved, but the components are brought together in four simple steps, with some help from a
handful of shortcut ingredients - like our sweet and smokey BBQ sauce for the glaze on the juicy chicken, and our creamy mayo
for the slaw. You're in for a treat!
